---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import marcusReesImage from '../assets/marcusrees.png';
---
<!doctype html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<BaseHead title="Marcus Rees - Tutor at New Leaf Academy" description="Meet Marcus Rees, a specialist tutor at New Leaf Academy." />
</head>
<body>
<Header />
<main>
<div class="bio-container">
<div class="bio-header">
<Image
src={marcusReesImage}
alt="Marcus Rees, Tutor at New Leaf Academy"
class="bio-headshot"
width={200}
height={200}
/>
<div class="header-text">
<h1>Marcus Rees</h1>
<p class="role">Specialist Tutor</p>
</div>
</div>

			<div class="bio-content">
				<h2>About Marcus</h2>
				<p>
					Marcus's passion for teaching began at a young age while working for Kumon during his school years, where he tutored younger students. He has been teaching and tutoring in some form ever since. 
				</p>
				<p>
					After achieving straight A's and A*'s at GCSE and A-Level, he went on to study Mathematics at the University of Bath, where he also completed his Master's degree. During his time at university, Marcus embraced a unique lifestyle, buying and living on a canal boat which he diligently restored. Alongside his studies, he worked at a farm and even ran his own market garden.
				</p>
				<p>
					He also completed a specific course on communicating mathematics during his time at university, which he credits as a key factor in becoming a highly effective and empathetic teacher.
				</p>
				<p>
					Currently, he is looking for a research job at Oxford University that would combine his interest in farming with his expertise in mathematics.
				</p>
				<p>
					Throughout all his endeavours, Marcus has consistently tutored a range of GCSE and A-Level students in the evenings. He has never let his busy life get in the way of his passion for helping others understand their way through school to academic success.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="cta-section">
				<h2>Ready to Start Your Journey?</h2>
				<p>Dan is ready to help you or your child achieve academic success. Book a friendly, no-obligation chat today.</p>
				<a href="/consultations" class="cta-button">
					Book Your Free Consultation
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
	<Footer />
</body>
</html>

<style>
:root {
--card-bg-color: #f9f9f9;
--box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

main {
	max-width: 900px;
	margin: 2em auto;
	padding: 0 1em;
	box-sizing: border-box;
	color: var(--accent);
}

.bio-container {
	background-color: var(--card-bg-color);
	padding: 2em;
	border-radius: 12px;
	box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
}

.bio-header {
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	align-items: center;
	text-align: center;
	margin-bottom: 2em;
	gap: 1em;
}

.bio-headshot {
	width: clamp(150px, 30vw, 200px);
	height: clamp(150px, 30vw, 200px);
	object-fit: cover;
	border-radius: 50%;
	border: 5px solid var(--accent);
	box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.header-text h1 {
	font-size: clamp(2em, 6vw, 2.8em);
	margin: 0;
	color: var(--accent);
}

.header-text .role {
	font-size: clamp(1.1em, 3vw, 1.3em);
	font-weight: bold;
	color: var(--accent-pop);
	margin-top: 0.25em;
}

.bio-content h2 {
	font-size: clamp(1.5em, 5vw, 2em);
	color: var(--accent);
	border-bottom: 2px solid #e9eafc;
	padding-bottom: 0.5em;
	margin-bottom: 1em;
}

.bio-content p {
	font-size: clamp(1em, 2vw, 1.1em);
	line-height: 1.8;
	margin-bottom: 1.5em;
}

	.cta-section {
	text-align: center;
	margin-top: 2em;
	padding: 2em;
	background-color: white;
	border-radius: 12px;
	box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
	color: var(--accent);
}

.cta-section h2 {
	font-size: clamp(1.5em, 4vw, 1.8em);
	margin-top: 0;
	color: var(--accent);
}

.cta-section p {
	margin-bottom: 1.5em;
}

.cta-button {
	display: inline-block;
	padding: 1em 2em;
	background-color: var(--accent-pop);
	color: white;
	font-weight: bold;
	text-decoration: none;
	border-radius: 8px;
	box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}

.cta-button:hover {
	transform: translateY(-5px);
	box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
	.bio-header {
		flex-direction: row;
		text-align: left;
		gap: 2em;
	}
}
</style>